Welcome to ForgeOS core-min - Minimal Linux for embedded devices

ForgeOS v0.1.0 core-min - Edge Computing Distribution
Built with security-first principles and minimal footprint.

Profile: core-min (BusyBox init, minimal services)
Access: Serial console only (ttyAMA0)
Networking: Loopback only (no external network access)

For documentation, see: /usr/share/doc/forgeos/
For support, visit: https://github.com/forgeos/forgeos

This system is configured for embedded/headless operation.
All security features are enabled by default.

